{"id": "rios002", "name": "Audio_YazawaRI_494_12_25", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "Rin, wake up!\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "...<i>*yawn*</i>... ~ ahhh, Dad?\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "What are you doing sleeping at the research institute? Don't you have class in the afternoon?\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Dad, did you forget? It's an exam day, we got off at noon.\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "... Oh, yea? I forgot.\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">I mentioned it at the table...</font>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "Yeah? What's the matter?\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Nuh-Nothing.\nWhat about Mom?\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "Asa's in the lab, I'm about to head there as well.\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Oh... Can I go watch?\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "No. The research into the florigen of Arabidopsis is entering its final stage. If the simulation of today's atomic structure is successful, it'll be a big step forward for us. Rin, just think about it. If humans could control the time that any flower blossomed... \n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "... Yeah, yeah, yeah, cut it out already! Dad, did you forget that your daughter's not a botanist!\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "Oh, okay... Anyway, we're gonna leave around 7 today. You wanna head home first?\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">But... nobody else is at home.</font>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "Rin?\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "... Whatever, I'll just wait until you're off. Can I do my homework in the lounge? Just like I used to.\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "Alright, I'll have an Architect take you there.\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Call Starts]</i>\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "Administration, this is researcher H7301 Yazawa Yasushi, please send an Architect over to escort a guest.\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Administrator]"], "content": "<i>This is Nakamura. Received. Dr. Yazawa, I'll arrange it immediately... Did Rin come for a visit?</i>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Hehe, Mr. Nakamura, good afternoon.\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "Apologies, sorry to bother you...\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Administrator]"], "content": "<i>Not at all, she's always been a good girl. She never bothers anyone. She even helps out occasionally. Oh, yea, Rin, did you get that album I asked you to pick up for me?</i>\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "... Nakamura, this is a public line, you know.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Administrator]"], "content": "<i>Ah, ahh hahaha... the Architect will be right there!</i>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Call Ends]</i>\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "Aigh... Rin, what kind of album did he ask you to get? It's not contraband, is it?\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Relax, it's just a folk album. It's a new album by an artist Mr. Nakamura likes. It's got an ancient feel, really unique! I'll let you have a listen later tonight! \n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "Your mother and I spend every day interacting with plants, we don't know anything about music. Forget it.\nAh, the Architect is here.\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "Footsteps"], "content": ""}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "Hello, Mr. Yazawa.\nI am Architect No. OPCII_0584_X, at your command.\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "Unit 10? Please escort my daughter to the lounge.\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Scan_01", "Scanning"], "content": ""}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "Report: Detecting Yazawa Rin's knee has suffered a minor scrap wound.\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "Eh? Really? What's the matter?\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Ah, this? It's nothing. I just fell down at the Academy, that's all. It'll be fine soon.\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "How do I not know about this?\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "I already told you...\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "Unit 10, pick her up and take her there.\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "Command received, executing immediately.\nMs. Yazawa, apologies.\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Eh? No need, I can do... wah!\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Move", "Picks Up Rin"], "content": ""}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "... it myself...\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "Nope. You need to rest before it heals.\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Robots' bodies are so... cold.\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "... Apologies.\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "......?\nI'd rather have my dad hug me.\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "Aigh... so affectionate.\nBut I gotta go find Asa.\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Ok... See you later, Dad~say hi to Mom!\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "Don't go running around.\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "凛！起きなさい！\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "ふわぁ～あ……んー……お父さん？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "なぜ研究所で寝ているんだ。\n午後の授業はどうした？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "パパってば忘れたの？\n今日はテスト期間だから学校はお昼まで。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "……そうだったか？\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">ごはんの時にこの話したのに……</font>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "ん？どうした。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "あ、ううん。なんでもない。\nお母さんは？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "研究室にいるよ。\nお父さんも今から行くところだ。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "んー……私も行っていい？\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "だめだ。\nシロイヌナズナの発芽メカニズムに関する研究はもう最終段階に入ってる。\n今日の分子結合シミュレーションに成功すれば、目標にまた大きく一歩近づく。\n凛、想像してみろ。もし人間が植物の開花を自由にコントロールできるようになったら……\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……わかった！わかったからストップ！\nお父さん、私植物学者じゃないから！\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "あ……っと、そうだったな……\nとにかくだ。\n今日は7時ごろまでここにいるだろう。\n先に帰らなくていいのか？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">家に帰っても……誰もいないもん。</font>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "凛？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……いいの。\nここで待ってる。\n休憩室で宿題やっててもいい？\n前みたいに。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "わかった。\nアーキテクトに送らせよう。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[通話開始]</i>\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "庶務課ですか？\n研究員ナンバーH7301、矢澤安（ヤザワヤスシ）です。\n客人の送迎用にアーキテクトを1体お願いしたいのですが。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[庶務員]"], "content": "<i>はい、庶務課中村です。\n承知いたしました。手配します。\n……矢澤博士、また凛ちゃんが来てるんですか？</i>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "えへへ～中村さんっ！\nこんにちは！\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "悪いな……よろしく頼む……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[庶務員]"], "content": "<i>大丈夫ですよ。\n凛ちゃんはいつもお利口にしててくれるんで、迷惑だなんて思ったことありませんから。\nそれどころか、たまにこちらのお手伝いをしてくれることもあって……\nそうだ、凛ちゃん、この前お願いしたアルバム、どうだった？</i>\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "……中村、今は社内通信中だぞ。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[庶務員]"], "content": "<i>うわ！\nあはははー……すぐにアーキテクトを手配します！</i>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[通話終了]</i>\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "まったく……凛、何のアルバムを頼まれたんだ？\n禁制品じゃないだろうな？\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "もう、そんなわけないでしょ。\n民族音楽のアルバム。\n中村さんの好きな演奏家さんの新作が出たからって頼まれてたの。\nなんか懐かしい感じ？っていうか、変わってる曲かな。\n夜にでも聞かせてあげるね！\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "お父さんもお母さんも毎日植物としか会話していないような生活だ。\n音楽なんてわからないからいいよ。\nあ、アーキテクトが来たな。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "足音"], "content": ""}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "アーキテクトナンバーOPCII_0584_X、ご命令をお待ちしております。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "10号機か？\n娘を休憩室まで頼む。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Scan_01", "スキャン"], "content": ""}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "レポート：矢澤さんはヒザに軽い擦り傷を負っています。\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "ん？なんだって？どうしたんだ？\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "あ、これ？\n大丈夫だよ！アカデミーで転んじゃって。\nでももう治りかけだから。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "なんで言わなかった？\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "言ったもん……\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "10号機、運んであげてくれ。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "承知いたしました。\n直ちに実行いたします。\n矢澤さん、失礼いたします。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "え？いいよ。\n私自分で歩け……きゃあ！\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Move", "抱き上げる"], "content": ""}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……自分で歩けるのに……\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "ダメだ。\nケガが治るまでは無茶はするな。\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "ロボットの身体冷たい……\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……申し訳ありません。\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……？\n私、お父さんに抱っこしてほしいな。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "まったく……いつになっても甘えん坊だな。\nでも、お父さんはもうお母さんの所へ行かなくちゃならない。\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "むぅー……わかった。\nじゃあ、また後でね。\nお母さんによろしくね！\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "みんなに迷惑かけるなよ。\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "凜，醒醒！\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "哈欠～啊，爸爸？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "怎麼跑來研究所睡覺？下午的課呢？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "爸爸忘了嗎？今天是測驗日，中午就放學了。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "……是嗎？我不記得了。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">明明就在餐桌上提過……</font>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "嗯？怎麼了？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "沒、沒有啦。\n媽媽呢？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "亞沙她在實驗室，我也準備要過去了。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "唔……我可以去參觀嗎？\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "不行。鼠耳芥的開花素研究已經進入最終階段了，今天的分子結構模擬如果成功，對於我們的目標會是一大進步。凜，妳想像一下，如果人類可以調控任何植物的開花時間……\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……好了好了，停！爸爸又忘記了，你女兒不是植物學家！\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "呃，好……總之我們今天會七點左右才走。妳不先回家嗎？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">家裡……也沒別人在啊。</font>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "凜？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……沒關係，我等你們下班。我可以去休息室寫作業嗎？像之前一樣。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "好，我讓建造者帶妳過去吧。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[通話開始]</i>\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "行政部，我是研究員編號 H7301 矢澤安，請叫一台建造者過來護送來賓。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[行政人員]"], "content": "<i>這裡是中村。收到了，矢澤博士，我馬上安排……是凜又跑來了嗎？</i>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "嘻嘻，中村先生午安。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "抱歉啊，又要麻煩你們了……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[行政人員]"], "content": "<i>沒關係啦，她一直都很乖，沒有打擾到其他人，偶爾還會幫大家的忙呢。對了，凜，上次託妳買的專輯買到了嗎？</i>\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "……中村，你現在是用公用線路通話。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[行政人員]"], "content": "<i>啊、啊哈哈哈哈……建造者馬上就到！</i>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[通話結束]</i>\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "真是的……凜，他要妳買什麼專輯啊？不是違禁品吧？\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "放心啦，是一張民俗樂專輯，中村先生喜歡的演奏家的新作。聽起來有種古老的感覺，很特別喔！晚上也讓你們聽聽看！\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "我跟妳媽每天跟植物打交道，不懂什麼音樂，算了吧。\n啊，建造者來了。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "您好，矢澤先生。\n建造者編號 OPCII_0584_X，聽候您的指令。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "十號機嗎？護送我女兒去休息室。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Scan_01", "掃描"], "content": ""}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "報告：偵測到矢澤凜小姐膝蓋部份有輕微擦傷。\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "咦？真的嗎？怎麼回事？\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "啊，這個？沒事啦，在學院不小心跌倒而已，已經快好了。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "我怎麼不知道？\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "這我明明也有說過……\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "十號機，那抱她過去吧。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "已收到指令，即刻執行。\n矢澤小姐，失禮了。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "咦？不用啦，我自己可以……哇！\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Move", "抱起"], "content": ""}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……我自己可以走啦……\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "不行，傷口好以前要好好修養。\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "機器人的身體……好冰。\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……不好意思。\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……？\n可以的話我比較想要爸爸抱我。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "唉，真愛撒嬌……不過我得去找亞沙了。\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "好啦。晚點見，幫我和媽媽問好！\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "別亂跑啊。\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "Rin, 일어나렴!\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "하~아암, 아빠?\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "왜 연구소에서 자고 있는 거니? 오후 수업은?\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "아빠, 까먹은 거야? 오늘이 시험이라서 오후엔 쉰다고.\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "...그러니? 기억이 안나서.\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">밥 먹을 때 분명 말했는데...</font>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "응? 왜 그러니?\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "아, 아니야.\n엄마는?\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "Asa는 실험실에 있어. 나도 이제 갈 준비를 해야겠구나.\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "응...나도 참관하러 가면 안 돼?\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "안 돼. 애기장대 개화 연구가 이미 최종 단계에 진입했거든. 만약 오늘 분자 구조 시뮬레이션만 성공한다면, 우리들은 한 걸음 더 목표에 다가갈 수 있단다. Rin, 상상해보렴. 만약 인류가 어떤 식물이든 개화 시기를 조종할 수 있다면...\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "...네~ 네~ 알았어요~ 이제 그만! 아빠 딸은 식물학자가 아니거든요!?\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "아, 그렇지...... 어쨌든 우린 7시 쯤에 돌아올 것 같구나. 너는? 먼저 집에 올 거니?\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">......집에 아무도 없는데, 뭘.</font>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "Rin?\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "......괜찮아. 아빠, 엄마 퇴근할 때까지 기다리지 뭐. 그럼 예전처럼 휴게실에서 숙제하고 있는 건? 그건 괜찮아?\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "그렇게 하렴. 아키텍트한테 널 휴게실로 데리고 가달라고 해두마.\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[통화 시작]</i>\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "행정과 계십니까? 저는 신분 번호 H7301 연구원 Yazawa Yasushi라고 합니다. 손님 호송을 위한 아키텍트 1대를 보내줬으면 합니다.\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[행정직원]"], "content": "<i>안녕하세요, 행정과 Nakamura입니다. 알겠습니다, Yazawa 박사님. 지금 바로 배정해 드리도록.... 또 Rin이 오는 겁니까?</i>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "히히, 안녕하세요, Nakamura 아저씨.\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "죄송하게 됐습니다. 저번처럼 잘 부탁드립니다....\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[행정직원]"], "content": "<i>괜찮습니다. Rin도 말을 얼마나 잘 듣는데요. 다른 사람 일하는 걸 방해하는 것도 아니고요. 게다가 가끔은 오히려 다른 사람을 도와주기도 하는 걸요. 아 참, Rin, 저번에 사달라고 부탁했던 앨범은 도착했니?</i>\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "......Nakamura 씨, 지금 공용 회선으로 통화 중인데...\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[행정직원]"], "content": "<i>아! 아하하하.... 아키텍트가 금방 도착할 겁니다!</i>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[통화 종료]</i>\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "하여간...... Rin, 너한테 무슨 앨범을 부탁한 거니? 금기품은 아닌 거지?\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "안심해~ 그냥 민요 음악 앨범 한 장 부탁한 것뿐이니까. Nakamura 아저씨가 좋아하는 연주가의 새앨범이거든. 들어봤는데 약간 고전적인 느낌이 들면서도 엄청 독특해! 저녁에 들려줄게!\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "나랑 네 엄마는 매일 식물들과 씨름하느라 음악 같은 거 잘 모르겠구나. 그러니 됐다.\n 오, 아키텍트가 도착했군.\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "발걸음"], "content": ""}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "안녕하십니까, Yazawa 씨.\n넘버링 OPCII_0584_X 아키텍트입니다. 지령을 내려주세요.\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "10호기인가? 내 딸을 휴게실로 데려다 줬으면 해.\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Scan_01", "스캐닝"], "content": ""}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "경고: Yazawa Rin 씨의 무릎 부위에 가벼운 찰과상 발견\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "뭐라고? 그게 정말이니? 어쩌다 그런 거니?\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "아, 이거? 괜찮아~ 아카데미에서 실수로 넘어졌는데 이제 거의 다 나았어.\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "다쳤으면 그래도 말하지 그랬니...\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "이것도 아빠한테 말했었는데...\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "10호기, 그럼 Rin을 안아서 그리로 데려가 주도록.\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "지령을 수령했습니다. 즉시 수행하겠습니다.\nRin 씨, 그럼 실례하겠습니다.\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "엥? 괜찮다니까! 나 혼자서도 걸을 수... 으앗!\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Move", "안아서 들어올린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "...혼자서도 걸을 수 있다니까...\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "안 돼. 상처가 다 나을 때까지는 그래도 최대한 조심하는 게 좋으니까.\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "아키텍트 몸은 또 왜 이렇게... 차가워.\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "...죄송합니다.\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "...? \n나는 아빠가 날 안고 데려다 주는 게 더 좋은데...\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "에휴, 정말 어리광은... 어쨌든 아빠는 이제 Asa한테 가봐야겠구나.\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "알았다구! 그럼 나중에 봐. 엄마한테 안부 전해주고!\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "함부로 뛰어다니고 그러지 말렴, 알았지?\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "凜，醒醒！\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "哈欠～啊，爸爸？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "怎麼跑來研究所睡覺？下午的課呢？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "爸爸忘了嗎？今天是測驗日，中午就放學了。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "……是嗎？我不記得了。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">明明就在餐桌上提過……</font>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "嗯？怎麼了？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "沒、沒有啦。\n媽媽呢？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "亞沙她在實驗室，我也準備要過去了。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "唔……我可以去參觀嗎？\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "不行。鼠耳芥的開花素研究已經進入最終階段了，今天的分子結構模擬如果成功，對於我們的目標會是一大進步。凜，妳想像一下，如果人類可以調控任何植物的開花時間……\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……好了好了，停！爸爸又忘記了，你女兒不是植物學家！\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "呃，好……總之我們今天會七點左右才走。妳不先回家嗎？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">家裡……也沒別人在啊。</font>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "凜？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……沒關係，我等你們下班。我可以去休息室寫作業嗎？像之前一樣。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "好，我讓建造者帶妳過去吧。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[通話開始]</i>\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "行政部，我是研究員編號 H7301 矢澤安，請叫一台建造者過來護送來賓。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[行政人員]"], "content": "<i>這裡是中村。收到了，矢澤博士，我馬上安排……是凜又跑來了嗎？</i>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "嘻嘻，中村先生午安。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "抱歉啊，又要麻煩你們了……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[行政人員]"], "content": "<i>沒關係啦，她一直都很乖，沒有打擾到其他人，偶爾還會幫大家的忙呢。對了，凜，上次託妳買的專輯買到了嗎？</i>\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "……中村，你現在是用公用線路通話。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[行政人員]"], "content": "<i>啊、啊哈哈哈哈……建造者馬上就到！</i>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[通話結束]</i>\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "真是的……凜，他要妳買什麼專輯啊？不是違禁品吧？\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "放心啦，是一張民俗樂專輯，中村先生喜歡的演奏家的新作。聽起來有種古老的感覺，很特別喔！晚上也讓你們聽聽看！\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "我跟妳媽每天跟植物打交道，不懂什麼音樂，算了吧。\n啊，建造者來了。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "您好，矢澤先生。\n建造者編號 OPCII_0584_X，聽候您的指令。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "十號機嗎？護送我女兒去休息室。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Scan_01", "掃描"], "content": ""}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "報告：偵測到矢澤凜小姐膝蓋部份有輕微擦傷。\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "咦？真的嗎？怎麼回事？\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "啊，這個？沒事啦，在學院不小心跌倒而已，已經快好了。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "我怎麼不知道？\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "這我明明也有說過……\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "十號機，那抱她過去吧。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "已收到指令，即刻執行。\n矢澤小姐，失禮了。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "咦？不用啦，我自己可以……哇！\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Move", "抱起"], "content": ""}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……我自己可以走啦……\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "不行，傷口好以前要好好修養。\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "機器人的身體……好冰。\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……不好意思。\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……？\n可以的話我比較想要爸爸抱我。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "唉，真愛撒嬌……不過我得去找亞沙了。\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "好啦。晚點見，幫我和媽媽問好！\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "別亂跑啊。\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "凛，醒醒！\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "哈欠～啊，爸爸？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "怎么跑来研究所睡觉？下午的课呢？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "爸爸忘了吗？今天是测验日，中午就放学了。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "……是吗？我不记得了。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">明明就在餐桌上提过……</font>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "嗯？怎么了？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "没、没有啦。\n妈妈呢？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "亚沙她在实验室，我也准备要过去了。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "唔……我可以去参观吗？\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "不行。鼠耳芥的开花素研究已经进入最终阶段了，今天的分子结构模拟如果成功，对于我们的目标会是一大进步。凛，妳想像一下，如果人类可以调控任何植物的开花时间……\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……好了好了，停！爸爸又忘记了，你女儿不是植物学家！\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "呃，好……总之我们今天会七点左右才走。妳不先回家吗？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">家里……也没别人在啊。 </font>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "凛？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……没关系，我等你们下班。我可以去休息室写作业吗？像之前一样。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "好，我让建造者带妳过去吧。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[通话开始]</i>\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "行政部，我是研究员编号 H7301 矢泽安，请叫一台建造者过来护送来宾。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[行政人员]"], "content": "<i>这里是中村。收到了，矢泽博士，我马上安排……是凛又跑来了吗？ </i>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "嘻嘻，中村先生午安。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "抱歉啊，又要麻烦你们了……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[行政人员]"], "content": "<i>没关系啦，她一直都很乖，没有打扰到其他人，偶尔还会帮大家的忙呢。对了，凛，上次托妳买的专辑买到了吗？ </i>\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "……中村，你现在是用公用线路通话。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[行政人员]"], "content": "<i>啊、啊哈哈哈哈……建造者马上就到！ </i>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[通话结束]</i>\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "真是的……凛，他要妳买什么专辑啊？不是违禁品吧？\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "放心啦，是一张民俗乐专辑，中村先生喜欢的演奏家的新作。听起来有种古老的感觉，很特别喔！晚上也让你们听听看！\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "我跟妳妈每天跟植物打交道，不懂什么音乐，算了吧。\n啊，建造者来了。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "脚步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "您好，矢泽先生。\n建造者编号 OPCII_0584_X，听候您的指令。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "十号机吗？护送我女儿去休息室。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Scan_01", "扫描"], "content": ""}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "报告：侦测到矢泽凛小姐膝盖部份有轻微擦伤。\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "咦？真的吗？怎么回事？\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "啊，这个？没事啦，在学院不小心跌倒而已，已经快好了。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "我怎么不知道？\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "这我明明也有说过……\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "十号机，那抱她过去吧。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "已收到指令，即刻执行。\n矢泽小姐，失礼了。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "咦？不用啦，我自己可以……哇！\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Move", "抱起"], "content": ""}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……我自己可以走啦……\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "不行，伤口好以前要好好修养。\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "机器人的身体……好冰。\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……不好意思。\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……？\n可以的话我比较想要爸爸抱我。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "唉，真爱撒娇……不过我得去找亚沙了。\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "好啦。晚点见，帮我和妈妈问好！\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Yasushi"], "content": "别乱跑啊。\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[讯号中断]</i>\n"}]]}